snippet.title: Anno 1800 Quick Tip&Trick #25 - How to get quickly "Anarchy is dead" & "The Better Anarchist"
snippet.description:
#Anno1800 #Tip&Trick #Anarchyisdead #Thebetteranarchist #killenemyai


Hey what's up everybody! it's pablo1713 Hi & Welcome to Anno 1800 Quick Tip&Trick #25 ! Today I will show you small trick on how to start a game and kill one of your enemy AI in the first minutes of your game :) What more you will see how I get my "Anarchy is Dead" and "The Better Anarchist" Achievements in like 5min xD :D Sooo yeah :D lots of fun and I did it live sooo you will see how my achievements will pop out on the screen :) 
I Hope you will find it interesting and useful :) 
Have fun! and enjoy the game without one enemy AI in your fresh new game and maybe with one of my best map seeds :P :) !

THX a lot everybody for subscribing! Love you ALL! :) :*
